Package io.github.ai4ci.output

Interface PersonTestsCSV

All Superinterfaces:
CommonCSV.Execution, CommonCSV.Model, CommonCSV.State, OutputWriter.Writeable
@Immutable public interface PersonTestsCSV extends CommonCSV.State
Individual test result records exported during simulation updates.

Main purpose: represent individual test events and their results. Records are produced during the UPDATE stage and are written per test event to a DuckDB database (cases.duckdb).

Downstream uses: case series, delay analysis, test sensitivity/specificity validation and contact tracing evaluation.

Author:
Rob Challen
